dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights.
Depth shown by bathymetric tints and soundings.
Includes text, timeline of major events between 1887 and 2011, and comparative area map. Shows boundaries, populated places.
Includes ancillary maps: Clan distribution -- Land use and economic activity -- Somaliland and Puntland -- Population density -- Indian Ocean Range Rings -- Neighborhoods of Mogadishu.
